replies.body:
I can see why they wouldn't disable him if it's a script.  Better to gather all the people who are using it and ban the accounts to try and deter people from using it till they can figure out a way to hotfix it.  I'm with the crowd tho, if you see someone pick Xerath, just dodge or use a Ban on him.  It's better to try and outplay an OP char than deal with Xerath exploits.  

Also, dodging games and a 5 min break isn't too bad unless you keep getting Xerath exploiters.  

{{champion:75}}
